<div class="title">Quitting</div>
<div class="substance">Caffeine</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=A.+Shaver&Exact=1">A. Shaver</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; A. Shaver. "Quitting: An Experience with Caffeine (exp24186)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jun 2, 2003. erowid.org/exp/24186</div>

